        <mxCell id="startup_fail_safe" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=14;" value="启动失败安全处理&lt;br&gt;标记 Bring-up Fault Active&lt;br&gt;强制关闭 BQ76200 执行层&lt;br&gt;关闭 BQ76940 CELLBAL，尝试关闭 CHG / DSG&lt;br&gt;CAN 0x305 上报 BringUp Fault，LED 故障提示" vertex="1">
